text: I reach this clinic at 7pm the women register me and I’m first time here she put me in the queue my number is 19 then she ask me to go n eat or drink outside the coffee shop after 35 minutes I return to the clinic and she told me that doctor cannot see cause already full this kind of clinic can treat patient like choosing vegetables
If you have a cough or fever, the doctor doesn't want to see you. If that is the case, then should put up a notice board to remind the public. And better not open the clinic.

Doc is always not around. was chased out by the auntie and ask me to go other clinic instead. Maybe better time to visit is around afternoon 1 pm. If doc is not around, pls don’t open the clinic. What’s the point of opening the clinic then.
Dr Soh is a very good doctor. Ethical and professional.
Don't give mc to students. Give a lot of excuse. Suppose to open at 11am but comes strolling in at 1130am. Like to tolak cases and didnt even bother checking me
